headline: Wynn Resorts (WYNN) Stock Trades Up, Here Is Why
summary: Shares of luxury hotels and casino operator Wynn Resorts (NASDAQ:WYNN) jumped 3.7% in the afternoon session after its Wynn Macau subsidiary was upgraded by analysts at UBS, citing an improved outlook for Macau's gaming revenue.
